lead_paragraph: Gonzaga center Przemek Karnowski missed almost all last season with a back injury, but he showed few signs of rust as he scored 14 points in the 14th-ranked Bulldogs' 92-69 victory over Utah Valley on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Melson Helps No. 14 Gonzaga Beat Utah Valley 92-69
